      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "OO"                 to   j-ope                  .
           move      "seq "               to   j-nam                  .
           move      f-xxx-pat            to   j-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mcvoju"
                                         using j                      .
       stp-srt-inp-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Start per numero distinta                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
